queries.sql: SELECT DATE(created_at) as d, COUNT(*) as c, SUM(total_usd) as s FROM `orders` WHERE `status` = 'paid' AND `created_at` >= '2025-11-08 00:00:00' AND `created_at` < '2025-12-08 00:00:00' GROUP BY DATE(created_at) ORDER BY DATE(created_at) ASC

SELECT p.name as product, SUM(oi.quantity) as qty, SUM(oi.price_usd * oi.quantity) as revenue FROM `order_items` `oi` JOIN `orders` `o` ON `o`.`id` = `oi`.`order_id` LEFT JOIN `products` `p` ON `p`.`id` = `oi`.`product_id` WHERE `o`.`status` = 'paid' AND `o`.`created_at` >= '2025-11-08 00:00:00' AND `o`.`created_at` < '2025-12-08 00:00:00' GROUP BY `oi`.`product_id` ORDER BY `qty` DESC LIMIT 5
